Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And I select 'Mammography' checkbox on Page 03
And	I'm on Page 04 of Mammography/Breast ultrasound
When	I select the radio button 'Bilateral normal imaging'
Then	the multiple choice Localization figure stays disabled

When	I select the radio button 'Obscured'
Then	the multiple choice Localization figure is enabled
When	I select 'R' part on the Localization figure
Then 'R' part turns red
When	I select 'L' part on the Localization figure
Then 'L' part turns red
And 'R' remains selected and red
